      <title>联合国机构称非洲主权债务超过 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/africa-has-over-1-trillion-in-sovereign-debt-un-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国一名官员称，非洲国家未偿还的主权债务超过 1 万亿美元，一些成员国难以偿还债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/africa-has-over-1-trillion-in-sovereign-debt-un-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 11:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
